'''叠氮化氟'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为FN<sub>3</sub>，它是一种黄绿色的[[气体|气体]]。<ref name="Gipstein1966">{{cite journal|last=Gipstein|first=Edward|coauthors=John F. Haller|year=1966|title=Absorption Spectrum of Fluorine Azide|journal=Applied Spectroscopy|volume=20|issue=6|pages=417–418|issn=00037028|doi=10.1366/000370266774386470}}</ref> 

叠氮化氟在–82℃液化，在–152°C变为固体。<ref name="Gipstein1966"/><ref name="Saxena2007">{{cite book|last=Saxena|first=P. B.|title=Chemistry of Interhalogen Compounds|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=nvatWdX1ZWcC&pg=PA96|accessdate=2014-06-16|date=2007-01-01|publisher=Discovery Publishing House|isbn=9788183562430|page=96}}</ref>

它在1942年由John F. Haller首次合成。<ref name="Lowe">{{cite web|url=http://pipeline.corante.com/archives/2008/10/21/things_i_wont_work_with_triazadienyl_fluoride.php|title=Things I Won't Work With: Triazadienyl Fluoride.|last=Lowe|first=Derek|date=2008-10-21|work=In the Pipeline|accessdate=2014-06-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613233159/http://pipeline.corante.com/archives/2008/10/21/things_i_wont_work_with_triazadienyl_fluoride.php|archivedate=2014-06-13}}</ref>

==制备==
叠氮化氟由[[氟气|氟气]]和[[叠氮酸|叠氮酸]]反应得到：<ref name=w /><ref name="Gholivand1987">{{cite journal|last=Gholivand|first=Khodayar|coauthors=Gabriele Schatte, Helge Willner|year=1987|title=Properties of triazadienyl fluoride, N3F|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=26|issue=13|pages=2137–2140|issn=0020-1669|doi=10.1021/ic00260a025}}</ref>
: 2 F<sub>2</sub> + 4 HN<sub>3</sub> → FN<sub>3</sub> + N<sub>2</sub> + NH<sub>4</sub>F

用[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]和氟气反应也能得到叠氮化氟。<ref name="Benard1989">{{cite journal|last=Benard|first=D. J.|coauthors=B. K. Winker, T. A. Seder, R. H. Cohn|year=1989|title=Production of nitrogen monofluoride (a1Δ) by dissociation of fluorine azide|journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry|volume=93|issue=12|pages=4790–4796|issn=0022-3654|doi=10.1021/j100349a022}}</ref>
==性质==
===化学性质===
在室温下，叠氮化氟分解而不发生爆炸：
: 2 FN<sub>3</sub> → F<sub>2</sub>N<sub>2</sub> + 2N<sub>2</sub>.<ref name="Gipstein1966"/>

而在高温下（例如1000℃），发生爆炸：
:FN<sub>3</sub> → FN{a<sup>1</sup>Δ} + N<sub>2</sub>. <!-- The FN{a<sup>1</sup>Δ} itself dimerizes on cooling. 2FN{a<sup>1</sup>Δ} → F<sub>2</sub>N<sub>2</sub>. --><ref name="Benard1989"/>

固体或液体FN<sub>3</sub>发生爆炸时放出热量，它的薄膜可以以1.6 km/s的速度燃烧。<ref name="Seder1991">{{cite journal|last=Seder|first=T.A.|coauthors=D.J. Benard|year=1991|title=The decomposition of condensed phase fluorine azide|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_combustion-and-flame_1991-06_85_3-4/page/353|journal=Combustion and Flame|volume=85|issue=3-4|pages=353–362|issn=00102180|doi=10.1016/0010-2180(91)90139-3}}</ref>

