===物理性质===
FN<sub>3</sub>的密度是1.3 g/cm<sup>3</sup>。<ref name="brener">{{cite book|last1=Brener|first1=Nathan E.|last2=Kestner|first2=Neil R.|last3=Callaway|first3=Joseph|title=Theoretical Studies of Highly Energetic CBES Materials: Final Report for the Period 2 March 1987 to 31 May 1987|url=http://www.dtic.mil/dtic/tr/fulltext/u2/a231340.pdf|accessdate=2014-06-25|date=December 1990|publisher=Louisiana State University, Department of Physics and Astronomy|pages=21–27|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170221/http://www.dtic.mil/dtic/tr/fulltext/u2/a231340.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

FN<sub>3</sub>可以在[[氟化钾|氟化钾]]的表面吸附，但却不能在[[氟化锂|氟化锂]]或[[氟化钠|氟化钠]]的表面吸附，这种性质被研究以便FN<sub>3</sub>可以增加固体推进剂的能量。<ref name="brener"/>

